Download and install XAMPP
Navigate to /XAMPP/htdocs folder, and copy all files from this repository into it (excluding the vaccineDB_Script.txt file)
Start XAMPP MySQL Database and Apache Web Server on host machine
Create a new database called CovidDB in phpMyAdmin
Import the vaccineDB_Script.txt file under the SQL tab
Navigate to the website by replacing the http://localhost:****/phpmyadmin/ with http://localhost:****/covid.html 
The website is now availible to browse and perform it's applications.
